  <source>GlaxoSmithKline</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this study is to assess the total CV risk in patients with type 2
      diabetes and also to assess the impact of rosiglitazone in the total CV risk and the
      parameters of metabolic syndrome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
